{"tid":83500,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"黑客工具銷情差很失望　Shadow Brokers 宣告「失陪」留 61 件道別禮物","createTime":"2017-01-16T19:00:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-27T07:23:42.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1c06aa39761ccb72d4a77ff304f4114948d8f509","tid":83500,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T19:00:59.000Z","msg":"去年神秘黑客 The Shadow Brokers 聲稱取得美國國家安全局的入侵工具，並放在網上拍賣，可惜銷情不理想，他們最終用中文對外界說「失陪」。雖然 The Shadow Brokers 已經隱退，但仍然接受拍賣付款，更再釋出 <span style=\"color: red;\">61 個 Windows 攻擊檔案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>作「道別禮物」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.pro/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/shadow-brokers-bye.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.pro%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2Fshadow-brokers-bye.png&h=ba63cc34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">「無人比 Shadow Brokers 更失望」</span><br />\n<br />\nThe Shadow Brokers 於去年八月聲稱入侵了一個與美國國家安全局有聯繫黑客組織 Equation Group，並拍賣獲得的入侵工具，包括 Fortinet 和 Cisco 防火牆的攻擊程式，不過這些工具的銷情並不理想。<br />\n<br />\n對此 Shadow Brokers 在上星期四聲稱「無人比他們更失望」，宣布道別和停止所有連聯渠道，更在 Twitter 用中文說「失陪」。然而他們的 BitCoin 地址依然有效，銷售活動仍會繼續。他們更指收到 10,000 Bitcoin 的話會釋出 Windows 和 Linux 的攻擊工具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n他們隱退前亦向外界釋出 61 個 Windows 攻擊檔案作「道別禮物」，當中有 43 個成功被卡巴斯基偵測為病毒。卡巴斯基其後證實，該些檔案主要是 EquationDrug 外掛程式、GrayFish 模組和 EquationVector 模組，是 Equation Group 使用的工具。<br />\n<br />\nThe Shadow Brokers 到底是何方神聖至今仍無人知曉。縱使他們用中文「失陪」來引退，外界普遍估計他們可能是俄羅斯人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.pro/2017/01/16/shadow-brokers-bye/news/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.pro%2F2017%2F01%2F16%2Fshadow-brokers-bye%2Fnews%2F&d=p7V8kcw7At%2BzUZ8v1VxoIUsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=820f89fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.pro/2017/01/16/shadow-brokers-bye/news/</a>"},{"pid":"dc2f099bf6344a8d7d6fec8ff7838ce8e90bf113","tid":83500,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T19:16:39.000Z","msg":"睇唔超大陸佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7fa70a8a31e1e96956a8a8500c4680c59e5ffcd","tid":83500,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T19:17:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇唔起大陸佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"8245f0aee18fa7661bd8222e99912b9e40bbab51","tid":83500,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T02:00:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"740f48c16e3353e7d5bea09e143e58791404c0a5","tid":83500,"uid":34500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T07:23:42.000Z","msg":"wfc"}]}